title: Patty Murray Faces Stiff Challenge From Tiffany Smiley in Senate Race
description: The five-term Washington senator is concerned about complacency among Democratic voters, who have come to regard her as a fixture who will always be there. She faces a Republican newcomer, Tiffany Smiley.
dc:creator: Emily Cochrane
media:credit: Lindsey Wasson for The New York Times
media:description: “We are a Democratic state,” Senator Patty Murray of Washington said. “If people vote.”
